<div class="bg-purple-900 py-16 -mt-1 w-full border-b-8 border-purple-800 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-white opacity-5 blur-3xl -mr-32 -mt-32"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-white italic uppercase tracking-tighter">Admin <span class="text-purple-300">Hub</span></h1>
        <p class="text-purple-200 mt-2 font-black uppercase text-xs tracking-widest leading-loose">Monitor. Atur. Kelola.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-20 -mt-32">
        <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border-b-8 border-purple-600 transition-all hover:scale-105 duration-500">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Total Users</h3>
            <p class="text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 tracking-tighter"><%= stats.users %></p>
            <a href="/admin/users" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 text-xs font-black italic uppercase tracking-widest mt-6 inline-block">Lihat Semua &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border-b-8 border-orange-600 transition-all hover:scale-105 duration-500">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Total Produk</h3>
            <p class="text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 tracking-tighter"><%= stats.products %></p>
            <a href="/admin/products" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 text-xs font-black italic uppercase tracking-widest mt-6 inline-block">Kelola Produk &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border-b-8 border-green-600 transition-all hover:scale-105 duration-500">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Total Pesanan</h3>
            <p class="text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 tracking-tighter"><%= stats.orders %></p>
            <a href="/admin/orders" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 text-xs font-black italic uppercase tracking-widest mt-6 inline-block">Proses Pesanan &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-purple-600 p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border-b-8 border-purple-800 transition-all hover:scale-105 duration-500 text-white flex flex-col justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-purple-200 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Quick Action</h3>
            <a href="/admin/products/add" class="py-4 bg-white text-purple-700 rounded-2xl font-black uppercase text-center tracking-widest text-sm hover:bg-purple-50 transition shadow-lg">+ Tambah Produk</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-[40px] p-16 shadow-2xl border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-purple-600 blur-3xl opacity-5 -mr-32 -mb-32"></div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-800 mb-10 uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight">Selamat Datang Chef Admin <br> <span class="text-purple-600">KenziemotoSport</span></h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-medium leading-relaxed max-w-2xl text-lg">Kelola semua operasional toko dari satu pusat kendali ini. Pastikan semua produk tersedia dan pesanan user diproses tepat waktu untuk performa bisnis yang maksimal.</p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mt-16 border-t border-gray-100 pt-16">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h4 class="text-xs font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Akses Cepat</h4>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                    <a href="/admin/orders" class="px-8 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all">Order Baru</a>
                    <a href="/admin/products" class="px-8 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all">Stok Produk</a>
                    <a href="/admin/users" class="px-8 py-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl transition-all">User List</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 bg-purple-50 rounded-3xl border border-purple-100 italic font-medium text-purple-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                "Kesehatan motor dimulai dari sparepart yang berkualitas. Tugas kita adalah memastikan keduanya sampai ke pelanggan."
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
